\s Mwokozi wetu anatupa furaha 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  wetu anatupa \bd*\bd Furaha \bd*\bd duniani, atuongoza kwa\bd*\bd  Neema \bd*\bd na anatushibisha. Tazama, yupo pamoja nasi,\bd*\bd  Neema \bd*\bd haitaisha kamwe! Haleluya, haleluya, haleluya, Amina! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ni vema kumpenda Mungu aliyetukomboa, vizuri kuwa mtu wake, sitapotea kamwe. Furaha yetu itabakia, ikiwa vyote vingetoweka. Haleluya, haleluya, haleluya, Aminia! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ikiwa giza mara nyingi, na jua likifichwa, na tukijaribiwa huku twajuwa ni kwa mda. \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd  hatutaona kamwe huzuni wala machozi tena. Haleluya, haleluya, haleluya, Aminia! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na tusisumbukie tena chakula wala nyumba, maana vyote twavipata kwa neâ€™ma yake Mungu. Njiani yote atuongoza aichukuwa mizingo yetu. Haleluya, haleluya, haleluya, Aminia! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ikiwa vema huku chini kutegemea \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , furaha gani huko juu kuona uso wake. Tutaiona furaha tele, na utukufu hautaisha, Haleluya, haleluya, haleluya, Aminia! \bd*
